comments: Strus (MIA) moves alongside LeVert's (CLE) path and avoids making arm contact as he contests during his fading jump shot attempt.
Herro (MIA) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes more than two steps before shooting.
Strus (MIA) jumps vertically as he contests the driving shot attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Mitchell (CLE) after the release.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a wide stance in Stevens's (CLE) path and delivers illegal contact that affects his ability to defend.
Butler (MIA) steps into Rubio's (CLE) path and delivers contact that dislodges Rubio (CLE) from his legally obtained defensive position.
Martin (MIA) establishes himself and firms up over his right foot in LeVert's (CLE) path and marginal body contact occurs as LeVert navigates over the pick.
Mitchell (CLE) swipes down and initiates arm contact with Martin (MIA) that affects his SQBR.
LeVert (CLE) is not established in Martin's (MIA) path when contact occurs, but the contact during the screen is marginal.
Adebayo (MIA) extends his left arm into Mitchell's (CLE) body and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Stevens (CLE) commits a take foul on Martin (MIA).
Butler (MIA) commits a take foul on Mitchell (CLE).
Love (MIA) and Lopez (CLE) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Okoro (CLE) reaches in and initiates arm contact with Butler (MIA) that affects his SQBR.
